Setup Steps


1. Create LINE Login Channel
LINE Developers Console
Create:
Provider
LINE Login Channel

NOT: Messaging API channel

2. Enable LIFF
Inside LINE Login channel:

Open “LIFF”
Add LIFF App

Example:

Endpoint URL:
https://liff-truckapp.vercel.app/

Scopes:

profile
openid

3. Add Callback URL
In LINE Login settings:
https://liff-truckapp.vercel.app/

4. Replace LIFF ID
liff id: 2010341226-BWVn7RwF

5. Deploy app on Vercel




3. Replace:
liff id: 2010341226-BWVn7RwF
with your actual LIFF ID.

4. host the frontend at Vercel


